value.0: Kobolds are small humanoids, dangerous only in great numbers.
Panels of hardened leather have been stitched onto the underlying rags. The leather has a sour smell, as if improperly cured.
This once fine burial armor now reeks of rot and decay.
Moss clings to the ancient stonework, slowly overwhelming it.

You found this crude burlap sack oozing blood atop an altar north of Brogan's Arm. Peering inside, you see the head of a long-dead dwarf. The kobolds must have claimed it from one of the zombies in the Meerwood.
Place this object in any area where you want tracking to occur.  Set Will to the DC of tracking in this area.
